                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-176-victim931 t18250113-176-viclabel933"></join>. On the 10th of January, about four o'clock, I saw the prisoner take the hat from a rail, at our door, and put it on his head, he ran off - I pursued him, and when I got within two or three paces of him, he threw it into the gutter - I sent for a constable, and secured him.</p>
